data.description: Unveil this meticulously remodeled 1948 home in Okanogan, Washington, with 2,451 sqft of modern comfort. Featuring 3 bedrooms, 2 baths, and ductless mini split heating and cooling, it's your serene haven. The country-style kitchen boasts all-new cabinets, butcher block countertops, and gleaming stainless steel appliances. Nestled on a 1-acre lot with riverfront, this property offers timeless charm and outdoor tranquility.  Make it yours today!
